# Purpose:
# - Prevent local-only files, secrets, build outputs, caches, and IDE metadata
#   from being committed to the repository.
#
# Must ignore:
# - Python virtual environments
# - __pycache__ and test caches
# - node_modules and frontend build output
# - .env files and local secrets
# - IntelliJ local workspace files
#
# Notes:
# - Repository hygiene matters early. Do not allow local machine state to pollute Git.

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# IDE
.idea/
*.iml

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
.env
.env.local
!.env.example

# Node
node_modules/
dist/

# Logs
*.log

# Docker
*.pid

# Secrets
secrets/*
!secrets/README.md
*.crt
*.key
*.pem
gcp-service-account.json

# Build artifacts
build/
coverage/
